# Billing System (FastAPI)

## Setup

1. Create virtual environment  
   `python -m venv venv`  
   `source venv/bin/activate`  (Linux/Mac) or `venv\Scripts\activate` (Windows)

2. Install dependencies  
   `pip install -r requirements.txt`

3. Create `.env` file with email credentials
EMAIL_USER=your@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-app-password
text4. Seed products (optional, run once)  
`python seed_data.py`

5. Run the app  
`uvicorn app.main:app --reload`

Open: http://127.0.0.1:8000/

Assumptions:
- Using SQLite (allowed in task)
- Product ID = auto-increment integer
- Change calculated in whole rupees only (paise ignored for simplicity)
- No fancy CSS, basic Bootstrap
- Email uses Gmail SMTP (use app password)